+++ UNITED FEDERATION OF PLANETS
+++ STARFLEET HEADQUARTERS
+++ STARDATE 52496.7
+++ ADMIRAL WESTMAN

Dear Captain G. VINCENT,

the USS HOPE (NCC-1731) has order to meet the USS ENTERPRISE
(NCC-1701-E) and the USS DEFIANT (NX-74205) to defend us against several
great invasion fleets some alien races sent to us!

Good luck, Captain!
