@node SCENARIOOVERVIEW
@title "What is in this scenario?"

@{b}OVERVIEW@{ub}

Estimated difficulty: Hard
Solvable with unregistered version: Maybe (not tested)

This one is really hard: Only two other ships are there to prevent
the enemies from just destroying the few starbases. You have only
short time to upgrade your ship since many starbases will missing
soon. Good thing although, the two other ships are the ENTERPRISE
and the DEFIANT and both are a little bit stronger this time, maybe
they will do a great job in also destroying some enemies...
_____________________________________________________________________

ENEMY UNITS

14x Klingon Battle Cruiser (K'T'INGA CLASS)    275
10x Romulan Warbird (D'DERIDEX CLASS)          300
 8x Cardassian Cruiser (GALOR CLASS)           300
 7x Dominion Warship (JEM'HADAR CLASS)         375
 1x Borg Cube                                 2200
_____________________________________________________________________

YOUR UNITS

 7x Starbase
USS ENTERPRISE (NCC-1701-E, SOVEREIGN CLASS)   425
USS DEFIANT (NX-74205, DEFIANT CLASS)          450
